name: gnuplot
raw_recipe:
{% set pkgname = "gnuplot" %}
{% set version = "5.0.5" %}
{% set sha256 = "25f3e0bf192e01115c580f278c3725d7a569eb848786e12b455a3fda70312053" %}

package:
  name: {{ pkgname }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ pkgname }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://sourceforge.net/projects/{{ pkgname }}/files/{{ pkgname }}/{{ version }}/{{ pkgname }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - gcc  # [linux]
    - pkgconfig
    - ncurses 5.9*
    - readline 6.2*
    - libgd
    - cairo 1.14.*
    - qt 4.8.*
    - pango 1.40.*
  run:
    - libgcc  # [linux]
    - ncurses 5.9*
    - readline 6.2*
    - libgd
    - cairo 1.14.*
    - qt 4.8.*
    - pango 1.40.*

test:
  files:
    - test-data.txt
  commands:
    - gnuplot -e "set terminal dumb; set style histogram; p 'test-data.txt'"
    - gnuplot -e "set terminal png"

about:
  home: https://github.com/gnuplot/gnuplot
  license: Gnuplot
  license_file: Copyright
  summary: Gnuplot, plotting from command line

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - croth1
